00:02:31.427 --> 00:02:34.459
It is necessary to work,

00:02:34.646 --> 00:02:38.310
To be faithful in very little things and faithful in much

00:02:38.886 --> 00:02:41.912
It's necessary to wait

00:02:42.333 --> 00:02:46.018
Hope is a companion

